河果邊<br />\n褔建幫UNDER中聯辦, 黑警唔會幫手<br />\n所以個人認為朝早行都冇問題, 但一定要入夜前走哂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:31:51.000Z","msg":"驚佢地朝早照打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住班黑警又話唔夠裝唔出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:36:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"325f1c8c9d467455c64014c00e3a9f2988b9b6be","tid":1431683,"uid":213949,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:39:46.000Z","msg":"仲有一個問題係發夢北角啲福建佬比人打緊嘅時候有人叫其他人走唔好過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下次再有咁嘅情況真係唔好阻人過去<br />\n點都過去幫拖啦我地咁多人<br />\n講左幾多次唔會開拖 但佢都一出手就即刻還拖？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a9335fab42465de70e35077e8ce0d1471a1b652","tid":1431683,"uid":73262,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:40:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}